            <h1>Python UI Developer , Львів</h1>

            <p><strong>PURPOSE OF THE JOB</strong>
</p>
<p>IronPort offers the C-Series Email Security Appliance, the S-Series Web Security Appliance and the M-Series Security Management Appliance. The core strengths of IronPort's solutions are IronPort's SenderBase®; the world's largest email and Web threat detection database, and AsyncOS® a customized operating system based on FreeBSD that has been designed from the ground up for application layer security. IronPort's products protect 8 of the 10 largest ISPs in the world, 3 of the 4 US Armed Forces, and more than 40% of the 100 largest corporations in the world. IronPort has also been recognized as an industry leader by every major industry analyst firm including the Gartner Group.
</p>
<p>UI team is responsible for design and implementation of Web user interface for managing appliance.
</p>
<p><strong><strong>MAIN TASKS AND RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></strong></p><ul> <li>Analyze feature requirements and write specification based on design provided by User-Experience team</li> <li>Develop Web UI interface using Python web-framework, front-end development using JavaScript and YUI framework.</li> <li>Obtain tasks from Team Leader supervisor and execute the tasks within set deadlines and specified quality objectives.</li> <li>Proactively address customer concerns and prevent problems from arising</li> </ul><p><strong>EDUCATION, SKILLS AND EXPERIENCE</strong></p><ul> <li>3+ years of extensive experience in web development using Python/PHP web-frameworks.</li> <li>Front-end development using JavaScript and JS-frameworks (YUI is a plus)</li> <li>Extensive knowledge of HTML, CSS, cross-browser compatibility, web security best practices, design patterns</li> <li>Working proficiency in Linux environment</li> <li>Experience working with Version Control Systems</li> <li>At least intermediate level of English</li> </ul><p><strong>PERSONAL COMPETENCIES</strong></p><ul> <li>Fast learning skills</li> <li>Result-oriented skills</li> <li>Responsibility</li> <li>Verbal/written communication skills</li> <li>Team-playing skills<strong></strong></li> <li>Personal motivation</li> </ul><p><em>Please send you CV on <a href="mailto:job_lviv@lohika.com" >job_lviv@lohika.com</a> or contact Lohika Recruitment Team with more questions!</em>
</p>
<p><em>You can also fill in <a href="fileadmin/Candidate_s_Form_for_website.docx" target="_blank" >Lohika Candidate's Form</a>.</em></p>
